<plot>A short 14 minute documentary on legendary director Stanley Kubrick ("2001", "A Clockwork Orange", "The Shining") covering his early career through his short works, through "The Killing", "Spartacus", "Paths of Glory", and "Lolita", to "Dr. Strangelove". Includes commentary on his work and exclusive photos, footage, and interviews.</plot><url>http://localhost:8983/solr/movie.html?540892</url></doc>
